    "109222424": {
      "title": "Gas Turbine Theory",
      "abstract": "1. Introduction. 2. Shaft power cycles. 3. Gas turbine cycles for aircraft propulsion. 4. Centrifugal compressors. 5. Axial flow compressors. 6. Combustion systems. 7. Axial and radial flow turbines. 8. Prediction of performance of simple gas turbines. 9. Prediction of performance - further topics."
